  "text": "The motive of this paper is to propose and present the experimental results of a grid-connected three phase FC system using vector control scheme. In this paper FC is use to produce electrical power. As the generated power is at low voltage level by using boost converter electrical power at higher voltage level is produced. The proposed three phase grid-connected FC system can operate either in grid connected or stand-alone mode [CITATION_1] .",
